<!DOCTYPE html>


<html data-theme="light" lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Slide 18 - Metricool vs Meta Business</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .slide-container {
            width: 1024px;
            height: 768px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .font-poppins {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .text-corporate-blue {
            color: #114a90;
        }
        .bg-corporate-blue {
            background-color: #114a90;
        }
        .text-corporate-red {
            color: #C0504D;
        }
        .bg-corporate-red {
            background-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .border-corporate-red {
            border-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .border-corporate-blue {
            border-color: #114a90;
        }
        
        .table-row-card {
            transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
            min-height: 140px;
        }
        .table-row-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.01);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border-left-width: 6px;
        }
        
        .col-tool { width: 30%; }
        .col-pros { width: 40%; }
        .col-cons { width: 30%; }
        
        .list-check li::before {
            content: "\f00c";
            font-family: "Font Awesome 6 Free";
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #10B981;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        .list-cross li::before {
            content: "\f00d";
            font-family: "Font Awesome 6 Free";
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #EF4444;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="slide-container font-poppins">
<header class="w-full h-24 flex items-end justify-between px-12 pb-4 relative z-10">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 bg-corporate-red"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
<span class="w-8 h-1 bg-corporate-red"></span>
<p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Gestión de Redes</p>
</div>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-corporate-blue">Metricool vs Meta Business</h2>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-end">
<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200">18</p>
</div>
</header>
<main class="flex-1 px-12 py-6 flex flex-col relative z-10 justify-center">
<div class="mb-8 w-3/4">
<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed">
                    Elegir la herramienta correcta es vital para optimizar tu tiempo. Analizamos las dos opciones principales para negocios locales:
                </p>
</div>
<div class="flex w-full px-6 py-4 bg-gray-100 rounded-t-xl border-b-2 border-gray-200">
<div class="col-tool">
<p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Herramienta</p>
</div>
<div class="col-pros">
<p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Lo mejor (Pros)</p>
</div>
<div class="col-cons">
<p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Limitaciones (Contras)</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
<div class="table-row-card flex w-full bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md items-center hover:border-l-pink-500 group">
<div class="col-tool flex items-center gap-4">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-pink-50 flex items-center justify-center text-pink-500 text-2xl group-hover:bg-pink-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
<i class="fa-solid fa-chart-simple"></i>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-start">
<p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xl">Metricool</p>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Todo en uno</p>
<a class="mt-2 px-3 py-1.5 border border-corporate-blue rounded-md flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-corporate-blue hover:text-white transition-colors group/btn" href="https://metricool.com/es/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-corporate-blue group-hover/btn:text-white m-0 transition-colors">Visitar web</p>
<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square text-[10px] text-corporate-blue group-hover/btn:text-white transition-colors"></i>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-pros pr-4">
<ul class="list-check text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
<li><p class="inline">IG + FB + TikTok incluidos</p></li>
<li><p class="inline">20 posts/mes (Plan Gratis)</p></li>
<li><p class="inline">Analíticas muy visuales</p></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="col-cons">
<ul class="list-cross text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
<li><p class="inline">LinkedIn es de pago</p></li>
<li><p class="inline">Límite de publicaciones</p></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="table-row-card flex w-full bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md items-center hover:border-l-blue-500 group">
<div class="col-tool flex items-center gap-4">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 text-2xl group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
<i class="fa-brands fa-meta"></i>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-start">
<p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xl">Meta Business</p>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Nativo de Facebook</p>
<a class="mt-2 px-3 py-1.5 border border-corporate-blue rounded-md flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-corporate-blue hover:text-white transition-colors group/btn" href="https://business.facebook.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-corporate-blue group-hover/btn:text-white m-0 transition-colors">Visitar web</p>
<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square text-[10px] text-corporate-blue group-hover/btn:text-white transition-colors"></i>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-pros pr-4">
<ul class="list-check text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
<li><p class="inline">IG + FB Ilimitado</p></li>
<li><p class="inline">Totalmente Gratis</p></li>
<li><p class="inline">Acceso a Inbox unificado</p></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="col-cons">
<ul class="list-cross text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
<li><p class="inline">Solo sirve para IG y FB</p></li>
<li><p class="inline">Interfaz a veces compleja</p></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 w-64 h-64 bg-corporate-blue opacity-5 rounded-tl-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>
<div class="absolute left-20 top-20 w-32 h-32 bg-corporate-red opacity-5 rounded-full blur-2xl -z-10"></div>
</main>
</div>

    <div style="position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; z-index: 9999; display: flex; gap: 10px; font-family: sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <a href="/slide-18" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Anterior</a>
        <span style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #fff; color: #333; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ccc;">19 / 26</span>
        <a href="/slide-20" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Siguiente</a>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>


